{"id": 2363, "genre": 1001, "title": "职场上为了留个好的第一印象，你都干过啥用力过猛的事儿？", "description": "上班第一天穿得过于老成，后来才知道大家当时都以为我是老同志返岗再就业。（图片来自：视觉中国）", "record_count": 2393, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20180521182942FT90uDUA35sZw6Eh.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-05-22T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 283137, "content": "职场不存在的，大学刚到宿舍的时候，给室友一人买瓶雪碧", "image": null, "praise_count": 43, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1351665}, {"id": 283141, "content": "不论说什么都笑，傻笑", "image": null, "praise_count": 201, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1350164}, {"id": 283142, "content": "看见人就说早安", "image": null, "praise_count": 124, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 667268}, {"id": 283143, "content": "装，隐藏自己，就真的没有自己了", "image": null, "praise_count": 108, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 966594}, {"id": 283399, "content": "尬聊，硬抛话题，可是没人接.....", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1297456}, {"id": 283146, "content": "神经比较大条没考虑过这种问题....一向都很随性，我好像发现了自己在公司人缘不好的原因了...", "image": null, "praise_count": 30, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 737718}, {"id": 283148, "content": "上班第一天讨好领导说要分担点工作，结果分下来发现自己不会，呵呵", "image": null, "praise_count": 75, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1108975}, {"id": 283150, "content": "刚来公司每天化淡妆，见人说早安，熟悉后就懒得化了?", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 582058}, {"id": 283151, "content": "多笑，多喝酒\n（*ﾟ∀ﾟ）つ―{}@{}@{}-　来吃烧烤♪", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1351281}, {"id": 283154, "content": "第一天上班，不管去干什么，都跑着去", "image": null, "praise_count": 59, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1340508}, {"id": 283155, "content": "满口答应老板，背后问底下的人:你明白老板什么意思吧？", "image": null, "praise_count": 48, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 935385}, {"id": 283667, "content": "告诉大家我的英文名：Cindy（我是男的）", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1136135}, {"id": 283668, "content": "告诉大家我很骚，超级gay", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1136135}, {"id": 283157, "content": "对老板抛媚眼，结果当晚，，", "image": null, "praise_count": 112, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1257902}, {"id": 283158, "content": "对上司和前辈毕恭毕敬，以至于他们觉得很尴尬。", "image": null, "praise_count": 111, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 36718}, {"id": 283159, "content": "说话的时候口齿不清，紧张到说错话", "image": null, "praise_count": 34, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1338154}, {"id": 283161, "content": "对老板上级说话的时候那叫一个小心迎合。", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1208211}, {"id": 283162, "content": "一厢情愿的热心肠，卖力不讨好的帮忙！", "image": null, "praise_count": 26, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 970221}, {"id": 283163, "content": "加班", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 717805}, {"id": 283164, "content": "得到“你真是个好人”的便利贴式评价", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1211155}, {"id": 283165, "content": "第一天化了妆为了给同事好印象，没想到要拍工牌照，幸好，之后就再也没化过，年会都没化。", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1196749}, {"id": 283168, "content": "天天加班", "image": null, "praise_count": 41, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1349542}, {"id": 283169, "content": "怂", "image": null, "praise_count": 54, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1226893}, {"id": 283170, "content": "不太想说话，但又不得不附和一下，最后导致自己很累", "image": null, "praise_count": 20, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1156796}, {"id": 283171, "content": "模仿对方说普通话的方言感", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1011020}, {"id": 283172, "content": "脸都笑僵了 ?", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1124984}, {"id": 288804, "content": "上班第一天无时无刻不在尬笑状态，抢着干活，很能干的样子", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1380759}, {"id": 283685, "content": "听着别人奉承领导的话，自己还要假笑", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1354185}, {"id": 283175, "content": "喊姐姐…我們總部都是女的", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1326408}, {"id": 283176, "content": "见谁都是名字➕职务 没职务的统统大哥大姐……", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1345747}, {"id": 283177, "content": "努力工作", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1351846}, {"id": 283946, "content": "对每个同事都用敬语，以及陪着配班老师加班（后面才知道原来她是为了等孩子每天不得已7点半走 我只是傻得以为要留下来加班 她也可得有人陪不戳穿……）", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1357108}, {"id": 283180, "content": "一直在说对不起和尬笑", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1305122}, {"id": 283182, "content": "脸盲的我差不多在一周内强行记住了所有人名字，特别是领导，见面一定会先打招呼并叫出姓和职位，同时还鞠躬。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1341220}, {"id": 283694, "content": "管谁都叫老师", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1160915}, {"id": 283695, "content": "每天穿高跟鞋", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1160915}, {"id": 283952, "content": "学会假笑，说违心话，看人眼色，压抑没有。。。总之，职场没办法……总要吃亏，总有一些恶心人恶心事情，得学会习惯！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1357234}, {"id": 283186, "content": "情绪激动，自我介绍连小时候养的猫叫啥都说出来了", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1017865}, {"id": 283187, "content": "见人喊老师好", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1017865}, {"id": 283188, "content": "下班时间不好意思走，等加班到最晚的同事走了才敢起身", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1017865}, {"id": 283190, "content": "叫姐……人家告诉我她98年的……", "image": null, "praise_count": 24, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1345254}, {"id": 283191, "content": "不懂装懂，结果把自己整蒙圈了，?", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1351971}, {"id": 283193, "content": "迎面走来个领导 一紧张叫错了名字", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1351980}, {"id": 283195, "content": "就是傻笑", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1352012}, {"id": 283196, "content": "迎合", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1351819}, {"id": 283197, "content": "10点上班,7:30就到了?", "image": null, "praise_count": 36, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1352017}, {"id": 283198, "content": "在新浪阅读上班的第一天为了表达重视，穿了我最贵的一件衣服，黑色呢子大衣上面有圈毛领，后，被全部门四个女性视为眼中钉，直到一年后离职依然不待见我（为什么是因为衣服，因为公司藏不住秘密）", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 716974}, {"id": 283201, "content": "明天周六你有空吗？有！", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1250694}, {"id": 283202, "content": "穿正装去互联网公司面试", "image": null, "praise_count": 18, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1021938}, {"id": 283204, "content": "额", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1352017}]}